[Given the recent occurrence of FMD serotype O in the Gaza strip and in Israel, it will be interesting to find out whether the sequencing of this latest serotype O in Jordan is a related strain. See comments in ProMED posting 20170221.4855322.

A map of the current situation of FMD in this area can be seen at http://tinyurl.com/z2nbngz (click on the section of interest on the map and zoom in). - Mod.CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4900918,9721.]
